text: Garcelles-Secqueville is a former commune. It is found in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2019, it was merged into the new commune of Le Castelet.Arrêté préfectoral 24 September 2018, p. 129 == References == Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Garcelles-Secqueville
